        <Text><![CDATA[
※ Please update in an environment where the Bluetooth connection is most stable.
* Please be careful not to update while in riding on vehicles, such as trains, or in environments where 2.4 GHz band radio waves such as Wi-Fi, microwave ovens, cordless phones and many other radio waves are intermingled.

※ Sony | Headphones Connect ※
Please update to the latest version before updating the main unit

[Update details in version 3.0.0]
It will optimize the headphones for the Google Assistant. 

[Notes]
※ Software update will optimize the headphones for the Google Assistant. Get help on the go using just your voice. Control your music, keep in touch with friends, set reminders, make dinner reservations and more - all without glancing at your phone.
1) Approximately 26 minutes (for Android), and 26 minutes (for iOS) are required for software update.
Never turn the "Power OFF" during update download, data transfer and updating.
If you do, the unit may become unusable.
2) Please update after confirming that these headphones and the Android device (or iOS device) have enough battery life.
3) If Bluetooth Low Energy devices (wearable terminals, smart watches, etc.) are connected to Android devices (or iOS devices), it may not be possible to update.
Please disconnect the connection of all Bluetooth devices and Android devices (or iOS devices) before updating.

[How to check the software version]
Select “WI-SP600N version" from the upper right menu of Sony | Headphones Connect application screen. 

